	(112,1,'2019-01-07 12:42:59','2019-01-07 11:42:59','[homeslider][/homeslider]\n\n[fullcontent]\n\n[aboutcouple title=\"About Elisa\" aboutimageurl=\"https://elisaesid-wp4.app/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/about_f.jpg\" readmorelink=\"\"]Love is friendship that has caught fire. It is quiet understanding, sharing and forgiving. It is loyalty through good and bad times. It settles for less than perfection and makes allowances for human weaknesses[/aboutcouple]\n\n[aboutcouple title=\"About Elisa\" aboutimageurl=\"https://elisaesid-wp4.app/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/about_m.jpg\" readmorelink=\"\"]Friends can help each other. A true friend is someone who lets you have total freedom to be yourself - and especially to feel. Or, not feel. Whatever you happen to be feeling at the moment is fine with them.[/aboutcouple]\n\n[/fullcontent]\n\n[weddingcountdown title=\"\" buttonurl=\"http://themes.sindevo.com/marriage-new/repondez-sil-vous-plait/\" buttontext=\"RSVP NOW\"][/weddingcountdown]\n\n[fullcontent]\n\n[onethirdcontent title=\"\"]\n<h2>Wedding Details</h2>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-17\" src=\"https://elisaesid-wp4.app/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/image13.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n\nLove is friendship that has caught fire. It is quiet understanding, mutual confidence, sharing and forgiving. It is loyalty through good and bad times. It settles for less than perfection and makes allowances for human weaknesses.\n\n[readmore url=\"http://themes.sindevo.com/marriage-new/repondez-sil-vous-plait/\"]READ MORE[/readmore]\n\n[/onethirdcontent]\n\n[onethirdcontent]\n<h2>Bachelor Party</h2>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-18\" src=\"https://elisaesid-wp4.app/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/image132.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n\nWe\'ve got this gift of love, but love is like a precious plant. You can\'t just accept it and leave it in the cupboard or just think it\'s going to get on by itself. You\'ve got to keep watering it. You\'ve got to really look after it and nurture it.\n\n[readmore url=\"http://themes.sindevo.com/marriage-new/the-wedding/\"]READ MORE[/readmore]\n\n[/onethirdcontent]\n\n[onethirdcontent]\n<h2>Wedding Decoration</h2>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-19\" src=\"https://elisaesid-wp4.app/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/image133.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n\nWe\'ve got this gift of love, but love is like a precious plant. You can\'t just accept it and leave it in the cupboard or just think it\'s going to get on by itself. You\'ve got to keep watering it. You\'ve got to really look after it and nurture it.\n\n[readmore url=\"http://themes.sindevo.com/marriage-new/the-wedding/\"]READ MORE[/readmore]\n\n[/onethirdcontent]\n\n[/fullcontent]\n\n[homecarousel title=\"Bridesmaids and Groomsmen\"][/homecarousel]\n\n[latestposts title=\"Journal\" posts=\"3\" category=\"journal\"][/latestposts]\n\n&nbsp;','homepage','','inherit','closed','closed','','4-autosave-v1','','','2019-01-07 12:42:59','2019-01-07 11:42:59','',4,'https://elisaesid-wp4.app/4-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
